CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Public Schools – Student Attendance – Excused or Discretionary Absences for
3 Civic Engagement
4 FOR the purpose of requiring the student attendance policy of the State Department of
5 Education and each county board of education to adopt a certain attendance policy
6 for public school students who are engaged in certain civic include a provision
7 allowing an excused or discretionary absence for a public school student participating
8 in civic engagement activities; requiring a county board to adopt certain policies and
9 procedures; and generally relating to student attendance in public schools and
10 excused or discretionary absences.
11 BY adding to
12 Article – Education
